flames and glad to finally be dry.
She hoped that later on she would be able to hunt and gather food, the 
Matrix knew just when Blaster was supposed to be healed yet.
But she had given him some of the most powerful concosions she had, and his 
recovery should be quick.

Zyber closed his eyes and moved into a more comfortable position, completely 
devoide of hearing DeathScyth raise himself from the bed and walk from the 
chamber...bent on seeking her out.*
